  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Stone Kin are dense, durable, and slow. Mundane weapons accomplish essentially nothing against their piercing and slashing immunity. They hold positions with the same commitment as Earth Elementals — put one in a doorway and it will be there when you return. Their Tremorsense gives them awareness of anything approaching through connected ground, which makes them difficult to ambush and reliable as sentinels even without active instructions.</p>"
