    "tactics": "",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Slam [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 2 + Melee Combat 4), Reach: 10 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 10 damage (Large, standard: 8 + 2)</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 15 damage (10 + 5 Str); target knocked Prone; no save</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 15 damage + Prone; target Restrained by erupting stone until they succeed on a Might check (Hard task, 2 successes) as a [Combat] action</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Rock Throw [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 2 + Ranged Combat 1), Range: 40/80 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 8 damage</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 8 damage; target knocked Prone</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Immovable:</strong> Cannot be knocked Prone by non-magical forced movement. Shoves automatically fail unless the attacker wins an opposed Strength + Athletics check (Hard task, 2 successes).</li>\n<li><strong>Earth Bond:</strong> While on natural earth or stone, regains 4 HP at the start of its turn. Suppressed if it took magical damage this round.</li>\n<li><strong>Powerful Build.</strong></li>\n</ul>",
